    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I hear you, but it feels like you're already deciding which side is right. If someone argues that a market-based system drives innovation and better technology through competition, shouldn't that be weighed equally against the social justice arguments? Or is the market-based approach inherently flawed in your view?",
